rows.label: qst105707_msg0002
rows.name:
Dad! Bahn did not...wish for...reunion!
Not like this... Mo mo!

rows.label: qst105707_msg0003
rows.name:
Sudden arrival take
Nilny by very surprise.

rows.label: qst105707_msg0004
rows.name:
Don promise to cooperate with
investigation if take to Bahn,
so Nilny bring Don here...

rows.label: qst105707_msg0005
rows.name:
But now so busy with running,
interrogation go nowhere!

rows.label: qst105707_msg0007
rows.name: Mo! Mo! Mo! Bahn cry...tears of happy!

rows.label: qst105707_msg0008
rows.name:
May take long time, but think problem
fixed now. Secrets of Lindwurm plot
against Empire finally come out.

rows.label: qst105707_msg0009
rows.name:
Nilny not thank friends
enough for helping.
